quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,70,"Nde Yuusufu yamirnoo golloo…ďe makko rimndude ngelooba musi…ó…ďe makko …ďen √Īaametee,o wa…ói etirgal laam…óo o etiraynoo ngal ka doŇčngal neene gooto makko on …ďe anndaali,fii no on heddora e takko makko.Nde …ďe fokkiti yiltitagol ka ma…ď…ďe noddoowo ewnii …ďe:Ko onon yo joomiraa…ďe ngelooba roondinba √Īaametee, ko on wuy…ďe ."
  12,71,"Musi…ó…ďe Yuusufa …ďen fewtiti e ewnii…óo on e wonndu…ďe e makko …ďen …ďe wi'i: Ko hon…óum majjiri on haa tuumiron min nguyka?"
  12,72,"Ewnii…óo on e wonndii…ďe makko …ďen wi'ani Yuusufa: Sari'yaare nde laam…óo on etirta nden majjirii men. Hino woodani kala addu…óo nde ado wi√Īeede, yeru doŇčngal ngelooba. Ko min fawtanii mo …óum."
  12,73,"Musi…ó…ďe Yuusufa …ďen wi'ani …ďe: Men woondirii Alla, gom…óii hi…óon anndi laa…ďugol amen e wo…ó…óondirgol amen e …óum, wano rentir…óon men. Hi…óon anndi kadi men ardaali ka leydi Msira fii bonnugol, men mee…óaali wonnde wuy…ďe e nguurndam amen."
  12,74,"Ewnii…óo on e wonndii…ďe makko …ďen wi'i: Ko hon…óum wonata njo…ďdi wujju…óo on e moo…óon si tawii ko on fenu…ďe e ko wii…óon kon hi…óon laa…ďi e wujjugol?"
  12,75,"Musi…ó…ďe Yuusufa …ďen wi'ani …ďe: Njo…ďdi wujju…óo woo e amen: wonnde kala mo ko wujjaa kon tawaa ka doŇčngal mun, o jonnitay hoore-makko wujjaa…óo on fii ko maccin…óina mo. Ko wano ndin njo…ďdi maccin…óingol …óon men yo…ďitirta wuy…ďe …ďen."
  12,76,"∆Āe artiri …ďe ka Yuusufu fii wittugol doŇčlle baaba-gootoo…ďe makko …ďen ado neene-gooto makko on fii suu…óugol feere nden. Refti o li√Īciti doŇčngal neene-gooto makko on, o yaltini ton sariyaare laam…óo on. Ko wano Men fewjirani Yuusufa non feere wa…óugol sariyaare nden ka doŇčngal neene-gooto makko on, men fewjirani mo kadi nanngitirgol musi…ó…ďe makko …ďen √Īaawoore leydi ma…ď…ďe ndin, maccin…óingol wujju…óo on. Si …ďe gollitirno √Īaawoore leydi laam…óo on Misra e hoore wujju…óo on, …ďe huutoray piggal e koondugol, si wanaa hara ko Alla muuyi feere goo, tawde ko O hattan…óo …óum. Me…óen …ďanta martabaaji on mo Men muuyani e jeyaa…ďe Amen …ďen, wano Men …ďantiri darja Yuusufa. Hino e dow kala jom-ganndal, ganndo goo …ďur…óo mo; hino e dow ganndal fow ngal kadi, ganndal Alla On anndu…óo kala huunde."
  12,77,"Musi…ó…ďe Yuusufa …ďen wi'i: Si o wujjii, haawnaaki, tawde neene-gooto makko on wujjiino ado oo …óoo wujjude -…ďe faandori …óum Yuusufa (yo o his)- Yuusufa suu…ói mette mum e konngol ma…ď…ďe ngol kon ka wonkii makko, o fe√Ī√Īinanaali …ďe …óum, o maaki e wonkii makko: Ko ngayngu mon ngun e kuu…óe mon bon…óe …óen ado hannde, woni bone on tigiri e oo nokku. Ko Alla non …ďuri anndude ndee fefindaare mon yaltunde e mon."
  12,78,"Musi…ó…ďe Yuusufa …ďen wi'ani mo: Ko an yo laam…óo on, oo no mari baabiraawo nayeeje …óoggos mo o yi…ói mo∆ī∆īa. ∆≥ettu gooto e amen lonto makko. Menen men yi'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe gollodal amen e wo…ó…ďe goo. Mo∆ī∆īan …óum …óon e amen."